Text.string: Oh, you've just made a big mistake.
Two hits, I hit you, you hit the ground!
You think you're a badass? Tch, we'll see about that.
I'll take this badass with six hands tied behind my back.
I hope for your sake you're as strong as you look.
A badass! I might actually break a sweat!
Like my trainer says, trust the process.
It feels good to be the best!
No one gets this good by staying humble.
Yes, it's me, I know, you're very impressed.
Is that the best you've got?
You can do better than that!
Hope you saved room for seconds!
There's more where that came from!
Did you think I was finished?
Well, that was a waste of time.
I was hoping there would be more.
A student of the "soft and weak" school of training, I see.
Well, look what I've got here!
This is a good one, I can feel it!
This is going to suck for you!
Imagine your pain as a ball of light. This one, to be precise.
Glad my trainer didn't see that.
Okay, you got me. Now it's my turn!
This is so terribly boring! Come on, Amara, happy place--punching bandits… punching skags… punching robots… ah, that's better.
A moment of tranquility. (deep inhale) Uuuuuugh! Let's gooo!
I've been flexing my abs for the last three days. I don't SEE my trainer… maybe it's safe to relax for just a moment… eh, better not risk it.
(pained hiss) Ah, yeah, there it is, my legs are cramping. I can't move my legs! Ugh, leg day, "just one more", "dig deep", cha! I'm gonna kill him the next time I see him!
Tigers were made to HUNT, NOT to stand around looking incredible! I've got places to be!
Guess I wasn't strong enough… this time.
Time to throw in the towel…
Should have kept my guard up.
